# Extreme distributed loads (per-unit-span)
# Source     : provided r/R flap-edge dataset (Fx -> q_y flapwise, Fy -> q_z edgewise),
#              interpolated to blade_spanwise_distribution.dat grid using
#              radial_pos / R_tip with R_tip = max(radial_pos).
# Convention : SI units (m, N, N*m). Per-unit-span quantities use "/m".
# Datum      : section frame; q_y is flapwise, q_z is edgewise, m_x is twist per unit span.
#
# Schema (in column order):
#   spanwise_pos   [m]       spanwise position z (matches blade_spanwise_distribution.dat grid)
#   radial_pos     [m]       radial position r from rotor centre
